des:
Forget those old annoying alarms! Wake up to the CHILLNESS of Wind Chime Alarm!

Wind Chime Alarm feature 2 free soothing and magical Wind Chime sounds and a unique snooze wind chime: "Tubular Fantasia," "The Witch's Dream," and "Belle du Jour." 

Get Wind Chime Gold to unlock seven MORE Wind Chime alarms including: "Deep Ring," Pretty Metal," "Tinkle Bell," "Light Ring," "Lazy Dayz," Bamboo Chimes," and a very special NEW chime- " Need Cowbell!"

All chimes are from 100% natural, organic, real-life recordings- not from synthesizers or AI algorithms. 

FEEDBACK AND SUPPORT: If you enjoyed Wind Chime Alarm, please leave us a review telling us what you love, and what alarms you want to hear next!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
